{"tid":346184,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 尼馬已經解約","createTime":"2017-08-03T17:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T08:26:33.000Z","uid":97997,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"949a99fc8c932b76a313b5b4f34901fbf1339afb","tid":346184,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"Barcelona forward Neymar has paid his buyout clause of 222m euros (&pound;200m), the Spanish club say.<br />\n<br />\nNeymar, 25, is set to sign for Paris St-Germain for a world record fee, after telling Barca he wanted to leave on Wednesday.<br />\n<br />\nThe Brazil international's lawyers paid the sum in person at Barca's offices.<br />\n<br />\nEarlier on Thursday, La Liga rejected an attempt to pay it the fee, over concerns PSG are violating Uefa's Financial Fair Play (FFP) rules.<br />\n<br />\nIn a statement, Barca said they &quot;will pass on to Uefa the details of the above operation so that they can determine the disciplinary responsibilities that may arise from this case&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nThe club said previously that they would report PSG to Uefa, European football's governing body, for a breach of FFP rules.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;On Thursday afternoon Neymar's legal representatives visited in person the club's offices and made the payment of 222m euros in the player's name with regards to the unilateral termination of the contract that united both parties,&quot; Barca's statement read.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/40814854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F40814854&d=oGzvDEhS3sglJcK%2BJ4WV9AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b5a9f157\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F40814854&h=8aee1463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/40814854</a>"},{"pid":"2aea74b20b14118f5d38ebf5fdd1f2761e8c1fe8","tid":346184,"uid":69805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:18:49.000Z","msg":"他媽的"},{"pid":"e50ca149c83ac1174368162e9ef4335d5d32faf8","tid":346184,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:20:14.000Z","msg":"【轉會SportsLight】<br />\n<br />\n巴塞隆拿官方網站宣佈，巴黎聖日耳門（PSG）所派出的律師代表團在當地時間下午抵達他們的辦公室，並且成功為尼馬支付了2.2億歐元的解約金。雖然西班牙甲級聯賽聯盟拒絕接收這筆費用，但是根據規定，只要雇主接收了解約金，那麼尼馬依然可以贖身。<br />\n<br />\n現在，尼馬只需要與PSG簽下合約，就會完成一切轉會手續，並趕及在本週法甲開鑼戰為PSG上陣比賽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=845943598889595&amp;id=493520410798584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D845943598889595%26id%3D493520410798584&d=oGzvDEhS3sglJcK%2BJ4WV9AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9fb2c09f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=845943598889595&amp;id=493520410798584</a>"},{"pid":"88346e69ddf6eaabe97e39e2a0365e8e4fc9fa70","tid":346184,"uid":43861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:21:31.000Z","msg":"已firm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4bf05b26a351668df6442b3617153dec7fa916","tid":346184,"uid":169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:21:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"456556dce38f2da11951ae83b76050c9fd112346","tid":346184,"uid":12154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"Cls...."},{"pid":"052d91ecc309179802248528c189c48359bc23f0","tid":346184,"uid":12154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:22:22.000Z","msg":"世界紀錄了"},{"pid":"edf6bb27b33a45f275a29d60b18da7d7a824c5ae","tid":346184,"uid":1953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"巴黎下一步會唔會搞青訓<